{"tid":1444264,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[忠告] 奉勸各位找換/提取外幣現鈔後，記緊保留收據！","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:01:10.000Z","uid":256019,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fec25149e1fdf31bdd1bbcedc7bbad4a1864ac11","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"我知好多巴絲同我一樣都係避險心態，換完外幣後有各式各樣打算，有存入離岸銀行戶口、有買美元資產、有keep現鈔，打算將來情況明朗化後存返入本地銀行，但無論決定係點，請記緊保留找換/提取收據，因為無論存離岸、本地戶口、匯款，職員都有可能要求你交待款項來歷，即是單據證明之類，否則職員可以以來歷不明款項理由拒絕處理 (防洗黑錢)，所以外幣從ATM提取，保留ATM單據、來自找換店就保留找換店收據，就咁簡單！未必一定要用，但如果需要證明，可以少好多麻煩！天佑香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f7b1649365e2dbbd0e79a7505d10c1429f4c5f","tid":1444264,"uid":33336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"月結單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d5ddfe9c4bbda39b85d5f3c23c6456cf30aae1","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f7b1649365e2dbbd0e79a7505d10c1429f4c5f","tid":1444264,"uid":33336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"月結單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"銀行可以有月結單，如果收e-statement就最好發出後即時將softcopy儲存或print hardcopy出黎，因為銀行e-banking通常只保留最新三至六個月e-statement (我恆生得三個月)，過後申請補發又要俾錢。"},{"pid":"75e35a6ed5e74a5bce11a23ff313010d16ef3f7c","tid":1444264,"uid":290911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒，未來幾日會去銀行換美金，雖然都係窮L一個"},{"pid":"a2c9305fa2b4d52aeb992d0df1602ce0ab67a757","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75e35a6ed5e74a5bce11a23ff313010d16ef3f7c","tid":1444264,"uid":290911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒，未來幾日會去銀行換美金，雖然都係窮L一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"我都係窮L，換完疊美元薄到可以做書箋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過信自己，決定就去做，唔使理人點睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9451c76ee05e2751e758a8d0276515d1eeb7ec0","tid":1444264,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"打簿ok ?"},{"pid":"c5995fff25c05a0c9588d84a0aff936f61fe8ada","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9451c76ee05e2751e758a8d0276515d1eeb7ec0","tid":1444264,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"打簿ok ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"外幣存摺？ok，總之有列出有關提取金額同日期都得，職員都係責任上問你拎證明，你俾到佢存檔就得，因為金管局會突擊抽查銀行、找換店、地產代理、保險公司之類，預防洗黑錢，資料不詳的話佢都有麻煩。"},{"pid":"b4e44085abaef6461aef115b0e716d5741ebbd35","tid":1444264,"uid":79602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d5ddfe9c4bbda39b85d5f3c23c6456cf30aae1","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f7b1649365e2dbbd0e79a7505d10c1429f4c5f","tid":1444264,"uid":33336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"月結單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"銀行可以有月結單，如果收e-statement就最好發出後即時將softcopy儲存或print hardcopy出黎，因為銀行e-banking通常只保留最新三至六個月e-statement (我恆生得三個月)，過後申請補發又要俾錢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"恆生如果係用電子月結單<br />\n可以有成24個月紀錄"},{"pid":"309e9ba3170297bca2c5483b5fb312fd7afda780","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5995fff25c05a0c9588d84a0aff936f61fe8ada","tid":1444264,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9451c76ee05e2751e758a8d0276515d1eeb7ec0","tid":1444264,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"打簿ok ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"外幣存摺？ok，總之有列出有